* Milestone 3  Text-to-Speech
PROBLEM faced on 27 of march 2026:{
    1. Text-to-Speech Issue:
    Initially, the model became slow after adding TTS because gTTS is network-based and blocks execution.
    This was solved by running TTS in a background thread, allowing OCR results to display instantly while audio is generated asynchronously.

    2. Speech Stopping Midway:
    The model stopped speaking due to unclean OCR text and long input handling by gTTS.
    This was fixed by cleaning the extracted text (removing broken words) and splitting it into smaller chunks before generating and combining the audio.
